<h2 class="blog--title">
<a href="/blog/2007/05/01/power-combination-sca-osgi-and-spring">Power Combination: SCA, OSGi, and Spring</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon engineering"></div>
<a class="category" href="/blog/category/engineering">Engineering</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<img class="meta-data--icon" src="https://gravatar.com/avatar/689563c501d5a959fccf03b707cb7b13?s=20&amp;d=mm" />
<span class="author">Adrian Colyer</span>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon calendar"></div>
<time class="date" pubdate="" datetime="2007-05-01 11:31:00.0">May 1, 2007</time>
